text: Kochnev or Kotchnev () is a Russian masculine surname, its feminine counterpart is Kochneva or Kotchneva. It may refer to *Aleksandr Kochnev (born 1987), Russian football player *Anna Kotchneva (born 1970), Soviet rhythmic gymnast *Yuri Kochnev (born 1942), Russian conductor of classical music Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Kochnev
